---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kebijakan Privasi">
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-green-100">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
      <div class="bg-green-600 rounded-full p-4 shadow-lg mb-3">
        <svg width="38" height="38" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#16a34a"/><path d="M8.5 12.5L11 15L16 10" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-green-700 mb-2 text-center">Kebijakan Privasi</h1>
      <div class="text-gray-500 font-medium text-center text-base md:text-lg max-w-md">Privasi Anda sangat penting bagi kami. Mohon baca kebijakan berikut.</div>
    </div>
    <ul class="space-y-4">
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="mt-1 text-green-600"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#bbf7d0"/><path d="M8.5 12.5L11 15L16 10" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">Data pribadi yang dikumpulkan hanya digunakan untuk keperluan pendidikan dan pengelolaan platform IniEdu.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="mt-1 text-green-600"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#bbf7d0"/><path d="M8.5 12.5L11 15L16 10" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">Kami tidak membagikan data pribadi pengguna kepada pihak ketiga tanpa persetujuan.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="mt-1 text-green-600"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#bbf7d0"/><path d="M8.5 12.5L11 15L16 10" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">Data pengguna disimpan dengan aman dan hanya dapat diakses oleh pihak berwenang di platform IniEdu.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="mt-1 text-green-600"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#bbf7d0"/><path d="M8.5 12.5L11 15L16 10" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">Pengguna dapat meminta penghapusan data pribadi dengan menghubungi admin IniEdu.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="mt-1 text-green-600"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#bbf7d0"/><path d="M8.5 12.5L11 15L16 10" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">Kami menggunakan cookie dan teknologi serupa untuk meningkatkan pengalaman pengguna di platform.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
        <span class="mt-1 text-green-600"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#bbf7d0"/><path d="M8.5 12.5L11 15L16 10" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        <span class="text-gray-800 font-medium">Dengan menggunakan platform IniEdu, pengguna dianggap telah membaca dan menyetujui kebijakan privasi ini.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="mt-10 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm">
      Terakhir diperbarui: 30 Mei 2025
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
